how_is_my_bmi



A small library to be able to generate your BMI Index - Body Mass Index.



Installation



pip install bmi



Get Started



How to get the BMI Index:



from bmi import Bmi



### Instantiate the BMI Object

user_2 = Bmi(105, 6)



### Call the BMI Calculator method

print(user_2.calc_bmi())

